    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 54-57.</p><p>Improved Legendary Smite</p><p>When you reach 24th level, your Legendary Smite’s range is increased to 45 feet. Regardless of whether the attack hits, all creatures in a 10-foot-wide line between you and the target, including the target, must make a Dexterity saving throw against your spell save DC, taking 70 (20d6) radiant damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p></div>",
